<img src = "cobra.jpg" width="300px" align="middle"> 
<p><ul>
<font color="black"><h3>Pose Information</h3>
<h4><li>Sanskrit Name : Bhujangasana</li>
<li>Pose Level : 1</li>
<li>Contraindications and Cautions</li>
Back injury<br>
Carpal tunnel syndrome<br>
Head ache<br>
Pregnancy<br>
</h3>
