    <li> Stretches chest and lungs, shoulders, and abdomen</li>
    <li>  Firms the buttocks</li>
    <li>Stimulates abdominal organs</li>
    <li>Helps relieve stress and fatigue</li>
    <li>Opens the heart and lungs</li>
    <li>Soothes sciatica</li>
    <li>Therapeutic for asthma</li>
    <li> Traditional texts say that Bhujangasana increases body heat, destroys disease, and awakens kundalini.</li>

</h4></ul></p></font>
